text.tspan: In order to cater to different layouts and usages, the four different typefaces are there to
cater an experience that are enjoyable for the users without loosing sights of what is important to them.

text.inkscape:label: Secondary color description
text.tspan: The color green and red should not be mistaken as part of the brand image, but a symbolic expression
of what Dealing Room is delivering: price fluctuation. The other colors are expressions that resemble
a classic tavern setting with a taste for classes.

text.inkscape:label: Identity color description
text.tspan: Simply black and white, however do not confused with
#000000 because of the overall softer brand image
comparing to the harder expression #000 brings.
